        What Does "As Is, Where Is" Mean When Selling Property in Brisbane?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The clause appears in specific types of property sales. It does not mean what many sellers think it means, and using it incorrectly can create serious legal exposure.
